    <h2>Description</h2>

    <p>
        Machina is a fan recreation of the level 0-Training from the original Deus Ex by Ion Storm.
        The goal is to learn Unreal Engine 5 by reproducing every aspect of this tutorial mission from the ground up in Unreal Engine and C++
    </p>

