                <li>Simple Interactable</li>
                <li>Complex Interactables & Mechanics</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Entities
            <ol>
                <li>Nonhuman Entities</li>
                <li>Passive Human NPCs</li>
                <li>Human Enemies</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Sounds
            <ol>
                <li>Sound Effects & Music</li>
                <li>Voice Acting</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>UI & Additional Mechanics
            <ol>
                <li>Diegetic UI</li>
                <li>Passive UI</li>
                <li>Active UI</li>
                <li>Minor Systems (Cutscenes, Save & Load, etc.)</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <p>
        While this process is still subject to change, it fairly clearly outlines my intentions in developing the project. 
        This is my most recently started project by far, and thusfar I have only completed phase 1.1, but progress is proceeding steadily.
    </p>
